snippet.title: Garden of Seif: Chronicles of an Assassin | OPENING VIDEO
snippet.description:
Garden of Seif: Chronicles of an Assassin is a narrative-driven otome game where choices matter. Play as an assassin navigating a world of danger, adventure, and romance, and a meddlesome fairy godmother. Will you play with evil intentions or will you forge genuine alliances?
